  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>This part silicone, part biological helmet can detect and replicate the facial muscle movements of the wearer, creating the appearance of a natural head. It is fully compatible with exosuit technology and provides all protection of a traditional helmet.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观覆盖</span>。<br><br>这个半硅质、半生物质的头盔能够检测和复制穿戴者的面部肌肉运动，创造出自然的头部外观。它与套装技术完全兼容，并能完全起到传统头盔的防护作用。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TencentChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>這半矽半生物的頭盔能偵測並複製穿戴者臉部肌肉的移動，做出頭部的自然外觀。與強化套裝科技完全相容，能提供傳統頭盔的所有防護。<br><br>能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變強化套裝的外觀。"
  },
